div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"ket-qua-bong-da-barcelona-chelsea-sieu-sao-choi-sang-loi-the-cuc-lon-c48a945148.html","id":"427"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 10:02 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chelsea h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n: \u201cSa ho\u00e0ng\u201d Abramovich h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n, tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Conte","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n\t\t <p>Khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i \u1edf Nou Camp vang l\u00ean, <strong>Chelsea</strong> ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 Champions League. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb g\u00ec l\u00e0 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn \u00f4m l\u1ea5y Lionel Messi - k\u1ebb v\u1eeba ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t \u201cThe Blues\u201d v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, k\u00e8m theo m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Dembele l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. Nh\u00ecn c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Conte n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Barca \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chelsea h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n: \u201cSa ho\u00e0ng\u201d Abramovich h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n, tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Conte - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Cap-nhat-Chelsea-Sa-hoang-Abramovich-hop-khan-trat-sa-thai-cho-Conte-4a331e9f00000578-5501573-image-a-28_1521066394523-1521072186-419-width660height494.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Conte vui v\u1ebb ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Messi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tin thua tr\u1eadn b\u00e1o v\u1ec1, \u1edf Stamford Bridge, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 lo s\u1eb5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho Antonio Conte. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 c\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf \u0111ang lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Conte. C\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Italia hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng, th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gh\u1ebf, thua tr\u1eadn th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ch\u00e2n gh\u1ebf n\u00e0o c\u00f2n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00ean b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Conte xem nh\u1eb9 bi k\u1ecbch s\u1eafp \u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd London Evening Standard cho hay, ngay khi Chelsea thua th\u1ea3m Barcelona 0-3, BL\u0110 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n \u1edf Stamford Bridge. Cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i do Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Marina Granovskaia hay Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bruce Buck ch\u1ee7 tr\u00ec, m\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Roman Abramovich \u0111\u1ee9ng ra \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh. N\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Antonio Conte, sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i London, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0o HLV Conte, v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201ch\u1ed5 l\u1ed1n\u201d c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. \u1ede tr\u1eadn thua Barca, bom t\u1ea5n Alvaro Morata - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Conte \u201cs\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebft\u201d \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn n\u00e9m \u0111i Diego Costa, l\u1ea1i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb trong th\u00e1ng 1 l\u00e0 Olivier Giroud \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Chelsea.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Bakayoko. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a HLV Conte khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y Conte sa \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Costa, sau n\u00e0y l\u00e0 David Luiz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u00fa h\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 <em>Chelsea</em> ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Chelsea hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5, \u00edt h\u01a1n Liverpool 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 Tottenham 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 trong 8 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y London s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Champions League m\u00f9a sau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Tottenham m\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Harry Kane, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y London v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft FA Cup v\u1edbi Leicester r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 18/3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chelsea h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n: \u201cSa ho\u00e0ng\u201d Abramovich h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n, tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Conte - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/Cap-nhat-Chelsea-Sa-hoang-Abramovich-hop-khan-trat-sa-thai-cho-Conte-roman-abramovich-conte-1-1955-1521072318-501-width660height518.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chelsea h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n: \u201cSa ho\u00e0ng\u201d Abramovich h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n, tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Conte - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">\u00d4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich (ph\u1ea3i) chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo London Evening Standard, HLV Carlo Ancelotti - ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y r\u1eddi Bayern Munich, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m trong vai tr\u00f2 HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n. \u201cCarletto\u201d s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Conte v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. Sau \u0111\u00f3, cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac, BL\u0110 Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV ti\u1ebfp theo. Hi\u1ec7n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 thay th\u1ebf Conte l\u00e2u d\u00e0i l\u00e0 HLV Luis Enrique - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;r\u1eddi Barcelona sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Luis Enrique s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i lu\u00f4n v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng <u>Chelsea</u> ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Antonio Conte, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd s\u1eb5n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng d\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 London l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 n\u0103m sau ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0a Chelsea \u0111\u0103ng quang Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Conte t\u1eeb thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eadn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"zone_banner_sponser_product\">\r\n                            \r\n                        </div>\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Barca h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Chelsea: B\u00e1o Anh \u201cquy ph\u1ee5c\u201d Messi, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-15/daily-mail-640x480-1521067214-459-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Barca h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Chelsea: B\u00e1o Anh \u201cquy ph\u1ee5c\u201d Messi, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>\u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Chelsea, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng khen Messi qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chelsea-hon-loan-sa-hoang-abramovich-hop-khan-trat-sa-thai-cho-conte-c48a945161.html","id":"426"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/03/2018 10:09 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Arsenal \u2013 AC Milan: \u201cPh\u00e1o\u201d quy\u1ebft n\u1ed5 to, \"r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t\" Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-09/thumbnail/960-1520600242-943-width640height480.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-48-945193\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mx